---
title: Double Shredded Chicken & Sweetcorn Soup with Roasted Veggies & Spring Onion
description: Just about every culture in the world has some version of hearty chicken soup, and it’s not hard to see why! There’s nothing quite as perfect on a cool night. This modern take on the soup is still perfectly fresh – we love the addition of zingy spring onion at the very end.
